 tiendas, omnipresentes en todo el pa\u00eds.\nSemanas atr\u00e1s, durante un acto al que asisti\u00f3 el ministro de Salud, Ramdev, que tambi\u00e9n posee una cadena de televisi\u00f3n, lanz\u00f3 un remedio con la marca Coronil que, seg\u00fan el gur\u00fa, cura covid-19.\nSu marca, 13\u00aa en el r\u00e1nking de popularidad en India, tambi\u00e9n afirma producir remedios contra el c\u00e1ncer.", "language": null, "image": "https://caracoltv.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/6c23e2d/2147483647/strip/true/crop/1024x538+0+0/resize/1200x630!/quality/90/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcaracol-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fc8%2F42%2F678b40204d799e8f8e88c4a906c1%2Fbaba-ramdev-afp.jpg", "pagetype": "article", "links": [null, "https://lakalle.bluradio.com/", "https://hjck.com/", "https://www.bluradio.com/blu360", "https://www.bluradio.com/", "https://www.bluradio.com/programas", "https://www.bluradio.com/nacion", "https://www.bluradio.com/blu360/bogota", "https://www.bluradio.com/politica", "https://www.bluradio.com/economia", "https://www.bluradio.com/deportes", "https://www.bluradio.com/mundo", "https://hjck.com/", "https://www.bluradio.com/noticias", "https://www.bluradio.com/entretenimiento", "https://www.bluradio.com/motor", "https://www.bumbox.com/", "https://www.bluradio.com/tecnologia", "https://www.bluradio.com/humor", "https://www.bluradio.com/blu360", "https://www.bluradio.com/medio-ambiente", "https://www.bluradio.com/programas", "https://www.bluradio.com/nacion", "https://www.bluradio.com/blu360/bogota", "https://www.bluradio.com/politica", "https://www.bluradio.com/economia", "https://www.bluradio.com/deportes", "https://www.bluradio.com/mundo", "https://hjck.com/", "https://www.bluradio.com/noticias", "https://www.bluradio.com/entretenimiento", "https://www.bluradio.com/motor", "https://www.bumbox.com/", "https://www.bluradio.com/tecnologia", "https://www.bluradio.com/humor", "https://www.bluradio.com/blu360", "https://www.bluradio.com/medio-ambiente", "https://lakalle.blu